					<div class="et_pb_section  et_pb_section_0 et_section_regular">
				
				
					
					<div class=" et_pb_row et_pb_row_0">
				
				<div class="et_pb_column et_pb_column_3_4  et_pb_column_0">
				
				<div class="et_pb_text et_pb_module et_pb_bg_layout_light et_pb_text_align_left c-breadcrumbs et_pb_text_0">
				
<div class="c-breadcrumbs" typeof="BreadcrumbList" vocab="https://schema.org/"><span property="itemListElement" typeof="ListItem" class="c-breadcrumbs__item"><a property="item" typeof="WebPage" title="Go to Terms and Conditions." href="/terms-and-conditions" class="post post-page c-breadcrumbs__link"><span property="name">Terms and Conditions</span></a><meta property="position" content="1"></span> &gt; <span property="itemListElement" typeof="ListItem" class="c-breadcrumbs__item"><span property="name" class="c-breadcrumbs__current-page">Privacy Policy</span><meta property="position" content="2"></span></div>

			</div> <!-- .et_pb_text --><div class="et_pb_text et_pb_module et_pb_bg_layout_light et_pb_text_align_left  et_pb_text_1">
				
<h1>8x8’s International Privacy Policies</h1>
<p>8x8, Inc. is committed to respecting our customers’ and prospective customers’ privacy. 8x8 has a privacy policy covering our current customers and one for prospective customers, which are linked below. Our privacy policies describe the information we collect and how we use and share that information.</p>
<p>In addition, 8x8, Inc. declares its commitment to the European Union-United States Privacy Shield Framework, as set forth by the U.S. Department of Commerce regarding the collection, use, and retention of personal information from European Economic Area member countries.&nbsp; 8x8, Inc. is also committed to comply with the United States-Swiss Safe Harbor framework governing the collection, use, and retention of personal information from Switzerland.&nbsp; 8x8, Inc. has certified that it adheres to the Privacy Shield Principles of notice, choice, accountability for onward transfer, security, data integrity and purpose limitation, access, recourse, enforcement, and liability. To learn more about the Privacy Shield program, to view 8x8 Inc.’s certification page, and to view a list of businesses that have self-certified compliance with the Privacy Shield, please visit <a href="https://www.privacyshield.gov/welcome" target="_blank">https://www.privacyshield.gov/welcome</a>.</p>
<p>Thank you for taking the time to review 8x8’s privacy policies.</p>
<p><a href="http://sims.8x8.com/GetDocument.aspx?docid=710791" target="_blank">Click here to read the 8x8 Privacy Policy for Customers (PDF)</a><br />
<a href="http://sims.8x8.com/GetDocument.aspx?docid=710776" target="_blank">Click here to read the 8x8 Privacy Policy for Prospective Customers (PDF)</a><br />
<a href="https://support.8x8.com/downloads/get/3673" target="_blank">Click here to read the 8x8 EU-U.S. Privacy Shield Framework Supplement to 8x8 Privacy Policies (PDF)</a></p>

			</div> <!-- .et_pb_text -->
			</div> <!-- .et_pb_column --><div class="et_pb_column et_pb_column_1_4  et_pb_column_1">
				
